data.title: Currency converter
data.meta_description: Currency converter: Get live conversion immediately with our currency converter. Simply input your amount and choose the currency and we will do the rest.
data.text:
World Currency Symbols

DNBC Financial Group introduces a list of worldwide currency symbols that are used to indicate that

a number has monetary worth, such as the dollar sign $, the pound sign , and the Euro sign

. This list is continually being updated, and we rely on user feedback to maintain it as

thoroughly

and accurately as possible.

DNBC has a complete list of ISO 4217 Currency Codes, which shows the standard three-letter codes

for every currency in the world.

DNBC Live Board Exchange Rates

The exchange rate is the value of other currencies compared to the US Dollar or Euro. These exchange rates are updated in real-time by The Currency Layer API. There will be differences depending on the currency you choose to exchange at the moment.
